title: Hour 2 – Was Tim Tebow An All-Time Bust? Guest – Dennis Lin
itunes:title: Hour 2 – Was Tim Tebow An All-Time Bust? Guest – Dennis Lin
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker sit in for Dan Patrick debate whether or not Tim Tebow is an all-time sports bust for failing in two different sports. They speak with Padres reporter Dennis Lin about the stellar offseason San Diego has had and whether or not they’ve closed the gap on the Los Angeles Dodgers.
